            <h2>Related Publication</h2>

            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <strong>Is your data supporting a publication? *</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <input type="radio" name="has_publication" id="has_publication_yes" value="true"
                           data-parsley-required="true"
                           data-read="true" data-read-type="single">
                    <label for="has_publication_yes" class="control-label" style="text-align:left; margin-right: 10px">
                        Yes
                    </label>
                    <br>
                    <input type="radio" name="has_publication" id="has_publication_no" value="false"
                           data-parsley-required="true"
                           data-read="true" data-read-type="single">
                    <label for="has_publication_no" class="control-label" style="text-align:left;">
                        No
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="publication_details" style="display:none;">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="publicationtitle" class="control-label col-md-4">
                        Title of your publication *
                    </label>
                    <div class="col-md-7">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="publicationtitle"
                               data-parsley-validate-if-empty="true" data-parsley-required-if-checked="#has_publication_yes" data-parsley-required-if-checked-message="This value is required"
                               data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-if-checked="#has_publication_yes"><br>
                        <p>If your data accompanies publication, please enter the tile of your publication. If your manuscript
                            is in preparation and you do not know the title yet, write 'TBC'.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="journal_name" class="control-label col-md-4">
                        Name of the journal *
                    </label>
                    <div class="col-md-7">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="journal_name"
                               data-parsley-validate-if-empty="true" data-parsley-required-if-checked="#has_publication_yes" data-parsley-required-if-checked-message="This value is required"
                               data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-if-checked="#has_publication_yes"><br>
                        <p>If your manuscript is in preparation and you do not know yet where it is going to be published, write 'TBC'.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="iscitedby" class="control-label col-md-4">
                        Link to your publication
                    </label>
                    <div class="col-md-7">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="iscitedby"
                               data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-if-checked="#has_publication_yes"><br>
                        <p>If you already have a link to your publication, please provide it here.
                            If the publisher has given you a DOI link for your publication, please enter the DOI here. Enter
                            just the DOI numbers (e.g. 10.17863/CAM.3). If you have a hyperlink without a DOI instead, please
                            enter the full hyperink, with the leading http instead.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <div class="form-group">
                    <div class="col-md-4" style="text-align: right;">
                        <strong>Is your publication already published? *</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-5">

                        <input type="radio" name="publication_published" id="publication_published_yes" value="true"
                               data-parsley-validate-if-empty="true" data-parsley-required-if-checked="#has_publication_yes" data-parsley-required-if-checked-message="This value is required"
                               data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-if-checked="#has_publication_yes">
                        <label for="publication_published_yes" class="control-label" style="text-align:left; margin-right: 10px">
                            Yes
                        </label>

                        <input type="radio" name="publication_published" id="publication_published_no" value="false"
                               data-parsley-validate-if-empty="true" data-parsley-required-if-checked="#has_publication_yes" data-parsley-required-if-checked-message="This value is required"
                               data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-if-checked="#has_publication_yes">
                        <label for="publication_published_no" class="control-label" style="text-align:left;">
                            No
                        </label>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="if_not_published" style="display:none">

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-md-4" style="text-align: right;">
                            <strong>Does your data need to be embargoed until your publication is published? *</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-5">

                            <input type="radio" name="embargo" id="embargo_yes" value="true"
                                   data-parsley-validate-if-empty="true" data-parsley-required-if-checked="#publication_published_no" data-parsley-required-if-checked-message="This value is required"
                                   data-read="true" data-read-type="single"  data-read-if-checked="#publication_published_no">
                            <label for="embargo_yes" class="control-label" style="text-align:left; margin-right: 10px">
                                Yes
                            </label>

                            <input type="radio" name="embargo" id="embargo_no" value="false"
                                   data-parsley-validate-if-empty="true" data-parsley-required-if-checked="#publication_published_no #placeholder_no" data-parsley-required-if-checked-message="This value is required"
                                   data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-if-checked="#publication_published_no #placeholder_no">
                            <label for="embargo_no" class="control-label" style="text-align:left;">
                                No
                            </label>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="if_embargoed" style="display:none">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="col-md-4" style="text-align: right;">
                                <strong>I understand that reviewers won't have access to embargoed files *</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-5">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="peerreviewaccess" id="peerreviewaccess" value="true" style="margin-top: 12px;"
                                       data-parsley-validate-if-empty="true" data-parsley-required-if-checked="#embargo_yes" data-parsley-required-if-checked-message="You must confirm"
                                       data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-if-checked="#embargo_yes">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="publication_date" class="control-label col-md-4">
                            Publication date (if known)
                        </label>
                        <div class="col-md-7">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control datepicker" id="publication_date"
                                   data-parsley-pattern="\d{4}-\d{2}-\d{2}" data-parsley-pattern-message="Please enter a date in the format YYYY-MM-DD"
                                   data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-if-checked="#publication_published_no">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

            <h2>Describe your data</h2>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="title" class="control-label col-md-4">
                    Title of your dataset *
                </label>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="title"
                              data-parsley-required="true"
                              data-read="true" data-read-type="single"><br>
                    Please enter the title of the dataset. For datasets supporting publications, the suggested title is "Research data supporting ['Tile of the publication']".
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-md-offset-4">
                    <h3>List all authors of this dataset</h3>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="authors_list">
                <div id="authors_0" class="repeatable_container">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="authors-0-given_names" class="control-label col-md-4">First name *</label>
                        <div class="col-md-7">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control repeatable-control" name="authors-0-given_names" id="authors-0-given_names"
                                   data-parsley-required="true"
                                   data-read="true" data-read-type="object-list" data-read-index-pattern="authors-(\d+)-.*" data-read-list-field="authors" data-read-field-pattern="authors-\d+-(.*)">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="authors-0-family_name" class="control-label col-md-4">Last name *</label>
                        <div class="col-md-7">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control repeatable-control" name="authors-0-family_name" id="authors-0-family_name"
                                   data-parsley-required="true"
                                   data-read="true" data-read-type="object-list" data-read-index-pattern="authors-(\d+)-.*" data-read-list-field="authors" data-read-field-pattern="authors-\d+-(.*)">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="authors-0-orcid" class="control-label col-md-4">ORCID</label>
                        <div class="col-md-7">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control repeatable-control" name="authors-0-orcid" id="authors-0-orcid"
                                   data-parsley-pattern="\d{4}-\d{4}-\d{4}-\d{3}[0-9X]" data-parsley-pattern-message="Please enter a valid ORCID"
                                   data-read="true" data-read-type="object-list" data-read-index-pattern="authors-(\d+)-.*" data-read-list-field="authors" data-read-field-pattern="authors-\d+-(.*)">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4" style="text-align: right">
                            <a href="#" id="orcid-less-more" data-state="closed">More about ORCID</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-7">
                            <div id="orcid-info" style="display:none">
                                Please enter your ORCID ID. Open Researcher and Contributor ID (ORCID) provides each academic
                                with a unique identifier, and is increasingly required by publishers and by data repositories
                                at the stage of research output submission. The use of ORCID ensures that each academic's
                                research activities are distinguished from those of others with similar names. Have a look
                                here for a <a href="http://osc.xxxxxxxx.ac.uk/author-tools/managing-your-online-presence/getting-orcid" target="_blank">video with instructions about getting ORCID</a>.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="authors-0-supervisor" class="control-label col-md-4">Supervisor?</label>
                        <div class="col-md-7">
                            <input class="repeatable-control" type="checkbox" name="authors-0-supervisor" id="authors-0-supervisor" value="true" style="margin-top: 12px;"
                                   data-read="true" data-read-type="object-list" data-read-index-pattern="authors-(\d+)-.*" data-read-list-field="authors" data-read-field-pattern="authors-\d+-(.*)">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="authors-0-supervisor" class="control-label col-md-4">This is me</label>
                        <div class="col-md-7">
                            <input class="repeatable-control thisisme" type="checkbox" name="authors-0-thisisme" id="authors-0-thisisme" value="true" style="margin-top: 12px;">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-md-7 col-md-offset-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-danger remove_author" id="remove_author" style="display: none;">Remove this author</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="col-md-7 col-md-offset-4">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary addanother add_author" id="another_authors" data-repeat-for="authors">Add another author</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-4">
                    <p>Please list the authors of this dataset and indicate who supervised this research.</p>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="description" class="control-label col-md-4">
                    Description of your data *
                </label>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <textarea class="form-control" id="description" style="min-height:200px;"
                              data-parsley-required="true"
                              data-read="true" data-read-type="single"></textarea><br>
                    <p>Where is this data from? What types of files are included in your dataset? Do your data support a publication? How were these data collected? Please also include any technical and non-technical information which will help in making these data accessible and reusable for the future.</p>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="keywords" class="control-label col-md-4">
                    Keywords *<br>
                    <small style="font-weight:normal;">
                        Enter at least 3 subject keywords or phrases, separated by commas (a maximum of 50 keywords or phrases can be entered).
                    </small>
                </label>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <div class="row" id="keywords_block" style="margin-bottom:5px;">
                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="keywords" id="keywords"
                                   data-parsley-required="true" data-parsley-pattern=".+,.+,.+" data-parsley-pattern-message="You must enter at least 3 keywords"
                                   data-read="true" data-read-type="single" data-read-value-separator=",">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4" style="text-align: right;">
                    <strong>Related resources</strong><br>
                    <small style="font-weight:normal;">If you would like us to link your dataset with other relevant existing resources (for example, your other existing publications, other datasets, external reports, webpages, news articles etc.), please provide URLs here.</small>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <div id="resources_list">
                        <div id="resources_0" class="repeatable_container" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                            <div class="form-inline">
                                <div class="form-group" style="margin-left: 0px; width: 100%">
                                    <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 5px">
                                        <div class="col-md-4"><label for="resources-0-type" class="control-label">Resource Type</label></div>
                                        <div class="col-md-8"><select class="form-control repeatable-control" name="resources-0-type" id="resources-0-type"
                                            data-read="true" data-read-type="object-list" data-read-index-pattern="resources-(\d+)-.*" data-read-list-field="resources" data-read-field-pattern="resources-\d+-(.*)">
                                            <option value=""></option>
                                            <option value="webpage">Webpage</option>
                                            <option value="sourcecode">Source Code</option>
                                            <option value="otherpublication">Publication</option>
                                            <option value="conferenceoutput">Conference Output</option>
                                            <option value="otherdataset">Dataset</option>
                                            <option value="report">Report</option>
                                            <option value="blog">Blog Post</option>
                                            <option value="other">Other</option>
                                        </select></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-4"><label for="resources-0-url" class="control-label">URL</label></div>
                                        <div class="col-md-8"><input type="text" class="form-control repeatable-control" name="resources-0-url" id="resources-0-url"
                                                                     data-read="true" data-read-type="object-list" data-read-index-pattern="resources-(\d+)-.*" data-read-list-field="resources" data-read-field-pattern="resources-\d+-(.*)">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <button class="form-control btn btn-danger remove_resource" id="remove_resource" style="display: none;">Remove</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-left: 0px;">
                        <p>Please enter the full URL, with the leading http</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-primary addanother add_resource" id="another_resources" data-repeat-for="resources">Add another resource</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4" style="text-align: right;">
                    <strong>Which funders are acknowledged for this research?</strong><br>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <div id="funder_list">
                        <div id="funders_0" class="repeatable_container" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                            <div class="form-inline">
                                <div class="form-group" style="margin-left: 0px; width: 100%;">
                                    <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 5px">
                                        <div class="col-md-4"><label for="funders-0-name" class="control-label">Funder name</label></div>
                                        <div class="col-md-8"><input type="text" class="form-control repeatable-control" name="funders-0-name" id="funders-0-name"
                                               data-read="true" data-read-type="object-list" data-read-index-pattern="funders-(\d+)-.*" data-read-list-field="funders" data-read-field-pattern="funders-\d+-(.*)">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-4"><label for="funders-0-project_id" class="control-label">Project ID</label></div>
                                        <div class="col-md-8"><input type="text" class="form-control repeatable-control" name="funders-0-project_id" id="funders-0-project_id"
                                            data-read="true" data-read-type="object-list" data-read-index-pattern="funders-(\d+)-.*" data-read-list-field="funders" data-read-field-pattern="funders-\d+-(.*)">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <button class="form-control btn btn-danger remove_funder" id="remove_funder" style="display: none;">Remove</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-left: 0px;">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary addanother add_funder" id="another_funder" data-repeat-for="funders">Add another funder</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


            <h2>About you</h2>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="given_names" class="control-label col-md-4">
                    First name *
                </label>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="given_names" name="given_names"
                           data-parsley-required="true"
                           data-read="true" data-read-type="single"><br>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="family_name" class="control-label col-md-4">
                    Last name*
